      "span_text": "Finally, the influence of buffer on the resonance Raman spectra supports the interpretation that alterations in Fe-His structure affect region I of mitoNEET. Recently, the crystal structure of mitoNEET in phosphate showed an interaction between His87 and a surface-bound phosphate molecule  with no evidence for buffer permeation into the protein or global conformational changes."
